COPY fsd_schema.about (about_id, about_type, about_info) FROM stdin;
1	History	Shantilal Shah Engineering College is affiliated to the Gujarat Technological University. It is approved by All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE), New Delhi and Government of Gujarat. The institute started functioning from the academic year 1983-84.
2	Vision	To become a leading engineering institute in the state, by developing excellent engineers capable of fulfilling needs of industry, society and nation at large.
3	Mission	To provide conducive academic environment motivating the aspiring engineers to achieve excellence.\nTo impart ethics and core values in graduates.\nTo promote contemporary infrastructure and external linkages
4	Why should you do PhD at IIT Bombay?	In our knowledge-centric society, there is an increasing appreciation for lifelong learning and the pursuit of knowledge, both for individual enrichment and societal advancement. Undertaking a Ph.D. represents a distinctive educational endeavor, marked by depth and commitment.
5	Research Opportunities:	Dive into a world of cutting-edge research across various disciplines. Work alongside renowned faculty members on innovative projects that push the boundaries of knowledge and shape the future.
6	Academic Excellence:	 Join a community dedicated to academic rigor and intellectual exploration. Our institute prides itself on fostering a culture of excellence, where scholarly inquiry thrives.
7	Faculty Expertise:	Our faculty members are leaders in their fields, bringing a wealth of expertise and experience to the table. Benefit from their mentorship and guidance as you navigate your PhD studies.
8	State-of-the-Art Facilities:	Explore our state-of-the-art research facilities and laboratories equipped with the latest technology. Access the tools and resources you need to conduct groundbreaking research and make meaningful contributions to your field.
9	Collaborative Environment:	Immerse yourself in a collaborative and interdisciplinary research environment. Connect with peers and faculty members across departments, fostering valuable collaborations and expanding your network.
10	Funding Opportunities:	We believe in supporting our students every step of the way. Take advantage of various funding opportunities. You can get this information at here academic website (link).
11	Professional Development:	IIT Bombay supports and encourages students to attend workshops, seminars, and conferences designed to help them succeed both academically and professionally.
12	Alumni Success Stories:	Join a community of successful alumni who have made their mark in academia, industry, and beyond. Hear their inspiring stories and discover the endless possibilities that await you after graduation.
13	Quality of Life:	Enjoy a vibrant campus life with access to comfortable housing options, recreational facilities, and campus amenities.
14	Diverse and inclusive environment:	Experience the supportive and inclusive environment that our institute is known for, both on and off campus.
15	Application Process:	Our application process is straightforward and transparent. Get all the information you need about admission requirements, deadlines, and application materials, and reach out to our admissions team for assistance at any time.
16	Structure of the program:	The Ph.D. program at IIT Bombay starts with a year of coursework, followed by a qualifying phase pairing students with advisors. This collaboration enhances scientific inquiry, knowledge acquisition, and technical skills. Candidates publish their research findings and prepare a thesis, scrutinized by a technical committee over 3-4 years, culminating in the compilation of research findings under advisor guidance.
17	   	To get more information on PhD courses, available programs, fees, application, and many more, please click here.
\.
